Introduction

Park Jongseong, known under his stage name Jay, is a South Korean-American singer-songwriter, rapper, dancer, and composer under Belift Lab. He is best known as a member of the boy group ENHYPEN.

On June 1, 2020, Jay was introduced as a contestant in the CJ E&M and BIGHIT MUSIC's reality survival show I-LAND. On September 18, 2020, he ranked as the 2nd place by global votes and became a member of ENHYPEN.

Jay made his debut as a member of ENHYPEN on November 30, 2020, with their first mini album "Border : Day One".
